830
00:57:20,730 --> 00:57:22,630
Shh!

831
00:57:22,630 --> 00:57:24,400
And the winner is...

832
00:57:24,400 --> 00:57:26,840
Joan crawford for
Mildred pierce!

833
00:57:26,840 --> 00:57:28,510
