854
00:58:36,580 --> 00:58:39,210
I love all of you!

855
00:58:39,210 --> 00:58:41,650
Miss crawford,
We love you!

856
00:58:41,650 --> 00:58:44,450
Now please forgive me.

857
00:58:44,450 --> 00:58:46,190
Good night.

858
00:58:56,200 --> 00:59:01,400
