What's wire hangers
Doing in this closet

861
01:01:06,290 --> 01:01:10,460
When I told you
No wire hangers?

862
01:01:10,460 --> 01:01:11,700
Ever!

863
01:01:13,230 --> 01:01:16,400
I work and work
Until I'm half dead,

864
01:01:16,400 --> 01:01:20,310
