01:02:27,270 --> 01:02:30,140
Why? Christina,
Get out of that bed!

891
01:02:31,840 --> 01:02:32,940
Get out of that bed!

892
01:02:32,940 --> 01:02:34,580
Oh!

893
01:02:34,580 --> 01:02:38,580
You live in
